{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "迦道夫（Fes限定Ver.） 第1话 亡国之君的回忆",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "本剧情涉及主线剧情\\n第19章的核心内容。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "是你啊。怎么了？\\n今晚应该是我巡夜才对啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "睡不着吗……\\n那不如听听我的往事吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "说起来，我似乎还没有和你们\\n仔细讲过我和席菈的身份。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "毕竟今后要一起行动，\\n所以我想我有必要\\n把我们的事讲清楚。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "是吗……那你且听我细细道来。\\n十几年前，我也曾是一国之君。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "十几年前\\n位于北方大陆的王国 勒福克斯",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（致我亲爱的朋友亚罗拉斯。\\n虽说已经入春，\\n勒福克斯却依然有些寒冷。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（或许是因为天寒，我偶尔会难以入眠。\\n这时我便会啜饮着妻子纳迪娅\\n所泡的红茶回顾往昔。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（最先浮现在脑海的便是\\n我在继承王位前为了历练\\n而与你一同游历世界的往事。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（古代遗迹、精灵森林……\\n我们一同遍览各地美景。\\n那时的震惊与感动，我永生难忘。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（时光流逝，\\n如今你我都成为了一国之君，\\n也都成为了一位父亲……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "爸爸，打扰了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "原来您在写信啊。\\n对方是不是就是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "嗯，是阿尔贝里亚的亚罗拉斯王。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "我一猜就是。\\n你们自从年轻时相识以来，\\n就一直保持着书信来往对吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "我和他算是战友。\\n不，应该说是损友吧。\\n你来这里是有什么事吗，席菈？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "我做了果馅饼来给您尝尝。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "噢，这次是挑战做点心吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "嗯。我拜托了厨师，\\n借了王宫的厨房一用。味道怎么样？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "嗯……不错。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "真的吗？太好了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "我记得你之前还试过种菜，\\n再之前是修家具对吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "虽说都不太像是王族会做的事，\\n不过你的爱好还真是广泛啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "这些可比唱歌跳舞实用多了。\\n而且，不是都说技多不压身吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "呵，你还真是个不走寻常路的王族。\\n让我仿佛看到了曾经的自己。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "参谋",
            "context": "打扰了，陛下。\\n南方的关隘发来报告称\\n有大批国外的人蜂拥而至。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "参谋",
            "context": "推测应是受巴尔特国的战火\\n牵连而逃来的难民。\\n请问此事该如何处置？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "命关隘打开城门，\\n然后做接收难民的准备。\\n我也会着手采取应对措施。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "参谋",
            "context": "遵命。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "又有其他国家的人们\\n逃难来了呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "我们勒福克斯一直都以中立的立场\\n保持着和平。这里在战乱不断的\\n北方大陆也算是一片安宁之地。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "他们正是对这个国家抱有希望，\\n才会拼死逃难到这里。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "那么无论是作为一国之君，\\n还是作为一个心怀仁慈的人，\\n我都不能不出手相助。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "爸爸……我可不可以也去\\n帮忙为接收难民做准备？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "因为我既是勒福克斯的王族，\\n也更是您的女儿。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "席菈……谢谢你。\\n那你便随我一同应对吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "嗯！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "勒福克斯原本是个安泰的国家。\\n然而自从发现领内拥有\\n稀缺的地下资源之后，\\n勒福克斯便成为了各国觊觎的对象。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "参谋",
            "context": "又有国家为了争抢资源\\n而向我们挑起战争吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "别抱怨了。\\n国家的和平要靠我们来维持。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01",
                "100042_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "所有人，打起精神来！\\n一同捍卫勒福克斯的领土！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "然而与此同时，国内各地\\n都观测到了黑暗魔力的出现。\\n为了应对被侵蚀的魔兽，\\n勒福克斯军早已疲惫不堪。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "就在军力最为空虚之时，\\n敌国趁机攻入。\\n勒福克斯也因此化作一片火海……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "纳迪娅！席菈！\\n你们在哪儿！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳迪娅",
            "context": "亲爱的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_1001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "坚持住啊！纳迪娅！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳迪娅",
            "context": "亲爱的……\\n一定要……照顾好席菈……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_1002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "纳迪娅……纳迪娅！\\n怎么会这样……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "呜……爸爸……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "席菈！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "爸爸……救命……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "好重的伤……\\n不过你别担心，我一定会救你的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "敌军这么快就攻到这里了……\\n席菈，抓紧我，我们离开这里。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01",
                "100042_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "眼看着祖国在烈火中燃烧，\\n我却只能抱着席菈逃离。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01",
                "100042_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "在那之后，我们和幸存的子民\\n一同藏身于森林之中。\\n而席菈她……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "爸爸……\\n勒福克斯还……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "勒福克斯已经沦陷了。\\n都怪我没有本事……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "这不怪爸爸……\\n爸爸不是已经为了\\n守护大家而奋战了吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "您是我……值得骄……傲的……\\n父亲……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "席菈？席菈！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "你醒醒啊，席菈……\\n要是连你都走了，我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "就在那时，\\n我看到了一只蝴蝶飞过。\\n那只蝴蝶唤醒了我往日的记忆。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（对了……那个男人\\n说不定能救活席菈。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（那个研究世间各类秘术的\\n精灵国之王一定会有办法的……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "参谋",
            "context": "陛下……您要去哪里？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01",
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "我要去找一位老朋友。\\n为了救席菈，我不得不去。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "我希望各位都能逃过此次劫难，\\n并找到安身之处。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "参谋",
            "context": "这里所有人都曾相信\\n勒福克斯是一个安居之地……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "参谋",
            "context": "然而如今勒福克斯已不复存在，\\n又何来的安居之地。\\n陛下，我们该去哪里才好……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01",
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "抱歉……现在的我似乎\\n回答不了你的这个问题。\\n请原谅我这个不称职的王……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "参谋",
            "context": "迦道夫陛下……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "身为一国之主，我本应为\\n流离失所的子民指引道路。\\n然而，当时的我并没有精力\\n去考虑那些事情。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "我带着全身冰冷的席菈\\n前往了精灵国。\\n为了寻求当时的精灵王\\n芬罗达的帮助。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_00_0070",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}